{"data":[{"date":"10:13 10/08","title":"H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c mua s\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a fan M.U th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng. M\u1ed7i khi h\u00e8 v\u1ec1, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u run s\u1ee3.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1ec1&hellip; photoshop<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 3 t\u00e2n binh Fred, Lee Grant v\u00e0 Diogo Dalot &ndash; 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m d\u00e0y b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, Jose Mourinho li\u00ean t\u1ee5c than v\u00e3n v\u00e0 ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea3 m\u00f9a h\u00e8, Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t k\u00eau g\u00e0o CLB mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb l\u1edbn t\u1edbi nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u00f4ng. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng k\u1ec3 ra nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire, Toby Alderweireld, Diego Godin, Jerome Boateng, Yerry Mina hay k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 Kurt Zouma &ndash; h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng Ivan Perisic hay Gareth Bale \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y m\u1eb7n m\u00e0 v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Sau c\u00f9ng, nh\u1eefng n\u1ebfp nh\u0103n tr\u00ean tr\u00e1n Mourinho ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng d\u00e0y h\u01a1n, v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u0111ang nh\u00ecn danh s\u00e1ch tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U m\u00e0 c\u00e1c fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u1ea1o ra v\u1edbi \u00e1nh m\u1eaft ao \u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/8.jpg\"></td>\r\n