le style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/12.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, PCT Ed Woodward th\u00edch th\u00fa v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i h\u01a1n</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than-172-194158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than-172-194158.html\">Mourinho h\u00e3y ng\u1eebng than v\u00e3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Tottenham l\u00e0 Tim Sherwood cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean than v\u00e3n v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho Man United.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-top-10-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-premier-league-172-194156.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/day-top-10-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-premier-league.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-top-10-ban-hop-dong-dat-gia-nhat-premier-league-172-194156.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Premier League</span><br>\r\nK\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/8. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 Top 10 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t Premier League m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nNguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2201","checkdouble":"194160"},{"date":"10:30 10/08","title":"C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Tottenham ch\u1eb3ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 bao, M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U b\u1ecb C\u0110V ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng mua ng\u01b0\u1eddi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 trung v\u1ec7 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng Jose Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 1 c\u00e1i t\u00ean trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u1eeda t\u00e1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u1ecd li\u00ean h\u1ec7. Trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1edd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00f4i k\u00e9o Diego Godin &ndash; m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, nh\u01b0ng anh v\u1eabn l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t nh\u1eefng Toby Alderweireld, Harry Maguire, Jerome Boateng v\u00e0 Yerry Mina \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi M.U, nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n sang \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c C\u0110V Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 ph\u1eabn n\u1ed9 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m c\u1ee7a BL\u0110, hay ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n l\u00e0 s\u1ee9c h\u00fat c\u1ee7a Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 b\u1edfi Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i Twitter:<br>\r\n</strong> &nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@SiisiKwesi: </strong></em>&ldquo;\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 t\u00f4i y\u00eau qu\u00fd th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@DeanJones:</strong> </em>&ldquo;R\u1ea5t th\u00edch h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Godin gia nh\u1eadp Old Trafford, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@truene:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y (Diego Godin). C\u1ee9 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Phil Jones m\u00e0 xem.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<em>&nbsp;</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@ekupnse:</strong></em><strong> </strong>&ldquo;Li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u00e0o c\u1ea5u Godin trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn b\u1ecb t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. CLB c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang ta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t n\u1ed7i h\u1ed5 th\u1eb9n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8\" title=\"Godin t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Godin t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<em><strong>@m16cam:</strong></em> &ldquo;Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea5y. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 m\u1ed9t ai \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00f9a.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>@adedayoice:</strong></em> &ldquo;T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U. Chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111ang x\u1ea3y ra v\u1eady?&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><em>@Bjohnson: </em></strong>&ldquo;Ch\u00fang ta b\u1ecb c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u1edfi Mourinho. N\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00f4ng ta ch\u00fat n\u00e0o. M.U c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i sa th\u1ea3i Mourinho ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?</span><br>\r\nBL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c mua s\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a fan M.U th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng. M\u1ed7i khi h\u00e8 v\u1ec1, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U l\u1ea1i...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than-172-194158.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-hay-ngung-than-van-va-chung-to-ban-than-172-194158.html\">Mourinho h\u00e3y ng\u1eebng than v\u00e3n v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV Tottenham l\u00e0 Tim Sherwood cho r\u1eb1ng Mourinho kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean than v\u00e3n v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1eadp trung g\u1eb7t h\u00e1i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho Man United.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u th\u00e0nh ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Old Trafford c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Premier League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2200","checkdouble":"194161"},{"date":"10:30 10/08","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 \u1edf ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/8/10/nhan-dinh-u23-nhat-vs-u23-thuy-dien-05h00-ngay-118-olympic-2016.jpeg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Spurs gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t bao g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Harry Kane. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Spurs \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/HLV-Pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n r\u1ea7u d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0o. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh&rdquo;, Pochettino n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 25 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Man United hay Man City. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CLB \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi (11/8), Tottenham s\u1ebd ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean Newcastle c\u1ee7a HLV Rafa Benitez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-tottenham-truoc-mua-giai-201819-nguy-co-vang-khoi-top-4-172-194053.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: Nguy c\u01a1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi Top 4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-he-2018-172-194040.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018: Mua kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i, b\u00e1n ch\u1eb3ng xong!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-that-vong-voi-world-cup-2018-172-193953.html\">Gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham-172-193924.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t, Pochettino v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2199","checkdouble":"194162"},{"date":"10:32 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valenciennes vs Chateauroux 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-valenciennes-vs-chateauroux-01h00-ngay-118-hang-2-phap-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Valenciennes vs Chateauroux l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valenciennes vs Chateauroux 01h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Valenciennes vs Chateauroux 01h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Valenciennes-vs-Chateauroux.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valenciennes vs Chateauroux</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Valenciennes vs Chateauroux</span></span></span></span></span></span>: 0-1</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1eb1ng 2 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eady nh\u01b0ng \u1edf cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Chateauroux t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Valenciennes l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 Valenciennes l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. C\u1ea7n nh\u1edb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 khi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau 19 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Chateauroux l\u1ea1i th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf 8/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Ri\u00eang tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng theo ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u1edf c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00eam 1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin v\u00e0o Chateauroux ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trong l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t vi\u1ebfng th\u0103m s\u00e0o huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Valenciennes. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1eefa c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Jean-Luc Vasseur \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng sau 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Valenciennes ch\u01a1i t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chateauroux b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn c\u00f3 2 b\u00e0n thua sau 4 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br>\r\n* 6 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Valenciennes \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm \u01b0u th\u1ebf v\u1edbi 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, trong khi Chateauroux ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i h\u00f2a 1 tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n* Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong s\u1ed1 3 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Valenciennes l\u1ea1i thua 2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chateauroux.<br>\r\n* 3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ebfp Chateauroux tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Valenciennes th\u1eafng 2, thua 1.<br>\r\n* L\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Valenciennes, Chateauroux \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 2-1.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2198","checkdouble":"194163"},{"date":"11:04 10/08","title":"Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: Max Allegri \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real Madrid m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 th\u00f4ng tin HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Allegri n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh HLV c\u1ee7a Real l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 c\u1ee7a r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia. Trong \u0111\u00f3, Julen Lopetegui th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh &ldquo;k\u1ebb ph\u1ea3n qu\u1ed1c&rdquo;, khi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c trong khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ed9t HLV kh\u00e1c llaijtwf ch\u1ed1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Zidane, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Max Allegri c\u1ee7a Juventus. Tuy nhi\u00ean, thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i CLB th\u00e0nh Turin. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, Allegri ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i v\u00ec cam k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi ng\u00e0i Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi Juventus khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Real &ndash; \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 l\u00e0 \u01b0\u1edbc m\u01a1 cho m\u1ecdi HLV. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus l\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid\" title=\"HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/tiet-lo-max-allegri-da-tu-choi-real-madrid-mua-he-nay.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t &lsquo;bandiera&rsquo; (bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a l\u00f2ng trung th\u00e0nh) nh\u01b0 Buffon hay Del Piero? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, hay mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho Juve, trong khi t\u00f4i m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m&rdquo; &ndash; Allegri k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a B\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0 th\u00e0nh Turin, Los Blancos c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t lu\u00f4n Cris Ronaldo v\u00e0o tay \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 115 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u1ec1 ph\u00eda thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Juve, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Allegri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real Madrid l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, khi \u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi CR7 v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus-176-194109.html\">Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf Real, Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/ronaldo-co-the-dua-juve-den-tam-cao-moi-176-194082.html\">Ronaldo c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a Juve \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi</span><br>\r\nBom t\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a Juventus m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Douglas Costa ca ng\u1ee3i Ronaldo s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2197","checkdouble":"194164"},{"date":"11:01 10/08","title":"Pochettino: \u201cTottenham gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4i l\u00e0 gi\u1ecfi l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i!\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/hlv-pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-tottenham.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. \u00d4ng tin r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Spurs gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tottenham chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t bao g\u1ed3m ch\u1ee7 c\u00f4ng Harry Kane. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1n ch\u00f3t c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Spurs \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eafn nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/8/HLV-Pochettino-phat-bieu-ve-chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Mauricio Pochettino ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 bu\u1ed3n r\u1ea7u d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0o. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh&rdquo;, Pochettino n\u00f3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 25 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, Man United hay Man City. Nh\u01b0ng trong nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh kh\u00e1c nhau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 CLB \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 18h30 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 7 t\u1edbi (11/8), Tottenham s\u1ebd ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a 2018/19. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean Newcastle c\u1ee7a HLV Rafa Benitez.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Tottenham tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-tottenham-truoc-mua-giai-201819-nguy-co-vang-khoi-top-4-172-194053.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Tottenham tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19: Nguy c\u01a1 v\u0103ng kh\u1ecfi Top 4</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chuyen-nhuong-tottenham-he-2018-172-194040.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Tottenham h\u00e8 2018: Mua kh\u00f4ng n\u1ed5i, b\u00e1n ch\u1eb3ng xong!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/harry-kane-that-vong-voi-world-cup-2018-172-193953.html\">Gi\u00e0nh Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng, Harry Kane v\u1eabn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pochettino-dat-muc-tieu-khong-tuong-cho-tottenham-172-193924.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t, Pochettino v\u1eabn \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2196","checkdouble":"194165"},{"date":"10:56 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ingolstadt vs Greuther Furth 23h30 ng\u00e0y 10/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-ingolstadt-vs-greuther-furth-23h30-ngay-108-hang-2-duc-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ingolstadt vs Greuther Furth l\u00fac 23h30 ng\u00e0y 10/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c Bundesliga II 2017/18): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ingolstadt vs Greuther Furth 23h30 ng\u00e0y 108 H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ingolstadt vs Greuther Furth 23h30 ng\u00e0y 108 H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Nhan-dinh-Ingolstadt-vs-Greuther-Furth.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ingolstadt vs Greuther Furth</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>Ingolstadt vs Greuther Furth: 1-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Greuther Furth \u0111\u00e3 tho\u00e1t ch\u1ebft v\u00e0o ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t, khi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 15 tr\u00ean BXH, \u0111\u1ee9ng ngay tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 play-off tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng nh\u1edd h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 ph\u1ee5. Sau c\u00fa ch\u1ebft h\u1ee5t n\u00e0y, BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea3i t\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean c\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c thanh l\u00fd 10 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, Greuther Furth \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1 9 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. Nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh \u0111ang h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp r\u1ea5t nhanh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Greuther Furth c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, khi th\u1eafng 2/3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a. S\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c 3-1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Ingolstadt, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu v\u1edbi m\u1ea1ch 6 tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng ngay tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua s\u1ea5p m\u1eb7t. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Ingolstadt \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111ang \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Ingolstadt, khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, b\u1edfi tinh th\u1ea7n c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111ang l\u00ean cao.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2195","checkdouble":"194166"},{"date":"11:23 10/08","title":"M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t: \u0110\u1ebfn \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/mu-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i Anh tr\u00f4i qua th\u1eadt nhanh. Song th\u00e0nh qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a Man United th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec 1 th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc: 2 b\u00e0n tay tr\u1eafng. Vi\u1ec7c M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJose Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i. Trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng th\u1ee9 5 (gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng), \u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o trong ng\u00e0y chi\u1ec1u mua c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c CLB gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBi\u1ebft v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 M.U v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 b\u00ed \u1ea9n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ee9c t\u1ed1c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. Ngo\u00e0i ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin n\u01a1i c\u00e1c Manucians sau chu\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec kh\u1ea3 quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0 c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/MU-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-Den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-Mourinho!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho t\u1eebng h\u1ee9a M.U ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i khi \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec3m 17h \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i l\u1edbn nh\u1ecf n\u00e0o gi\u01a1 cao chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u M.U, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd h\u1eb3n \u0111an xen c\u1ea3m x\u00fac h\u1ee5t h\u1eabng c\u1ed9ng b\u1ef1c b\u1ed9i. L\u00fac \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0 l\u00e0m g\u00ec. Nh\u01b0ng tin ch\u1eafc n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc b\u00faa trong tay, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1eadp n\u00e1t b\u00e0n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Mourinho nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eeb l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U h\u00e8 n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Fred \u2013 1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Diogo Dalot \u2013 1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh 19 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 Lee Grant \u2013 1 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u00e3 35 tu\u1ed5i. Kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec h\u01a1n. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn thi\u1ebfu \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 1 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u00e0 1 m\u0169i c\u00f4ng c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fred\" title=\"Fred\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Trong 3 t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a M.U ch\u1ec9 Fred c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u c\u1ee7a M.U trong ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u1eeda s\u1ed5 mua s\u1eafm t\u1ea1i Anh c\u0169ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ed1c. Nh\u1eefng Harry Maguire, Toby Alderweireld, Yerry Mina, Jerome Boateng r\u1ed3i c\u1ea3 Diego Godin \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc t\u00ean song kh\u00f4ng ai \u0111\u1eb7t g\u1ea5p m\u00e1y bay t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh Manchester.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00e0nh t\u00edch thua 2, h\u00f2a 3 sau 6 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00f3i l\u00ean r\u1eb1ng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u s\u00e2u. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 \u1edf 3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn HLV Mourinho kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng d\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft tr\u00fat gi\u1eadn l\u00ean Godin, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t giao k\u00e8o m\u1edbi v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u1eeb Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng l\u00fac n\u00e0y Mourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1edbi Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Anthony Martial. Kh\u00f4ng ai d\u00e1m kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u1ebft th\u00e1ng 8, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i gia ngo\u00e0i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o. Ch\u00ednh vi\u1ec7c M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u00f3 khi l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd so\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t l\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n xin ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba Barca\" title=\"Pogba Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Mourinho-tiet-lo-Paul-Pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u1ed5 c\u1ee7a Mourinho</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Matthew Judge h\u1eb3n l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mourinho mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf m\u00e0 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u. \u0110\u00e1ng n\u00f3i \u1edf ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede c\u1ea3 2 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft M.U, Mourinho \u0111\u1ec1u n\u1ed9p danh s\u00e1ch c\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea7n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u01b0a khi n\u00e0o \u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng v\u1eady, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho va Woodward\" title=\"Mourinho va Woodward\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/mu-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ee7a Woodward c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang l\u00e0 M.U \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed9 th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1ea1i. Tay \u00e1o c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ean c\u1ee7a Kohler \u2013 m\u1ed9t h\u00e3ng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb gia d\u1ee5ng. H\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c MoPlay v\u00e0 h\u00e3ng r\u01b0\u1ee3u Chivas Regal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00fang ph\u1ea3n \u00e1nh \u01b0u ti\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 gi\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 M.U h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. T\u1eeb n\u0103m 2005 khi nh\u00e0 Glazers mua l\u1ea1i CLB v\u00e0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ea5p t\u00e0i s\u1ea3n v\u1edbi l\u00e3i su\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, nh\u1eefng ho\u00e0i nghi r\u1ed3i ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. 8 n\u0103m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sir Alex Ferguson d\u1eabn d\u1eaft, M.U v\u1eabn c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. Nh\u01b0ng sau khi \u00f4ng ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u, \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?</span><br>\r\n<span>BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong vi\u1ec7c mua s\u1eafm, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a fan M.U th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u1eebng. M\u1ed7i khi h\u00e8 v\u1ec1, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tin \u0111\u1ed3n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U l\u1ea1i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, M.U tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng. C\u00e1c HLV nh\u01b0 David Moyes, Louis Van Gaal v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 Mourinho nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t \u00edt s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1eeb nh\u00e0 Glazers c\u00f9ng ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o. N\u1ebfu ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecdn gi\u1eefa t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 m\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, tin ch\u1eafc h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn v\u1ebf \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e0ng qu\u00fd, Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Woodward c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a M.U \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tay b\u1eaft m\u1eb7t m\u1eebng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng l\u1ee3i \u00edch to l\u1edbn v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a CLB. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 N\u1eeda \u0111\u1ecf th\u00e0nh Manchester ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a trong c\u00e1c cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd th\u1eeba bi\u1ebft \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 Woodward t\u1eebng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi 3 th\u00e1ng th\u00ec \u201chi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kinh doanh c\u1ee7a M.U\u201d. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho s\u1ef1 th\u1edd \u01a1 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng c\u00f9ng c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 cho nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi th\u1ec9nh c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Mourinho. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebfn l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a 99% M.U c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y h\u01a1n 1 tu\u1ea7n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u00f2 h\u1ec1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nha Glazers\" title=\"Nha Glazers\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Nha-Glazers.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u00e0 Glazers t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh l\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 c\u1ee7a Mourinho t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111i theo chi\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng x\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00e3 th\u1ebf, khi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u1edfi tranh, \u00f4ng v\u00e0 M.U c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc. \u0110\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Man City c\u00f3 \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d Riyad Mahrez, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i th\u00e8m kh\u00e1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nLiverpool c\u00f3 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Chelsea chi 123 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Jorginho, Kepa c\u00f9ng m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1ec1 Mateo Kovacic. Arsenal c\u0169ng s\u1edbm ch\u1ed1t 5 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho h\u1ecd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2h r\u1ea1ng s\u00e1ng mai (11/8), M.U s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng cu\u1ed9c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 c\u1ea3m kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh l\u1ea1i \u00f9a v\u1ec1. C\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i th\u00f4i, \u0111\u1ebfn \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho c\u01a1 m\u00e0\u2026<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham-172-193964.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham-172-193964.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Premier League 2018/19: Mou m\u00f9a 3 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea3m?</span><br>\r\n<span>Jose Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ee5 n\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m NHA 2018/19 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cac-muc-tieu-tu-choi-mu-la-loi-cua-mourinho-172-194161.html\">C\u00e1c m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i M.U l\u00e0 l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Mourinho</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hai-huoc-ai-bao-mu-khong-co-tan-binh-nao-mua-he-nay-172-194160.html\">H\u00e0i h\u01b0\u1edbc: Ai b\u1ea3o M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718-172-194127.html\">Mourinho: \u201cM.U \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 NHA ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec\u2026 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2194","checkdouble":"194167"},{"date":"11:44 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh St.Pauli vs Darmstadt 01h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-stpauli-vs-darmstadt-01h30-ngay-118-hang-2-duc-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>St.Pauli vs Darmstadt l\u00fac 01h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c Bundesliga II 2017/18): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh StPauli vs Darmstadt 01h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh StPauli vs Darmstadt 01h30 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 \u0110\u1ee9c 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-St-Pauli-vs-Darmstadt-hang-2-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">St.Pauli vs Darmstadt</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span>St.Pauli vs Darmstadt: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 \u1ed5n t\u1ea1i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi 2018/19. V\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n trong khi Darmstadt \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n Paderborn tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 th\u00ec St. Pauli c\u0169ng h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Magdeburg tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng th\u1ebb, gi\u1eefa St. Pauli v\u00e0 Darmstadt c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c. St.Pauli \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n ch\u00fat \u00edt b\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u1ecd c\u00f3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, ch\u1ec9 ch\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 St. Pauli c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khu\u1ea5t ph\u1ee5c Darmstadt. N\u00ean bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch \u0111ang c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00ec Darmstadt \u0111\u00e3 15 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eafng 6/7 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra, th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 s\u1edf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e0ng tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o Darmstadt.Qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng St. Pauli d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p d\u1edbp m\u1ed7i khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Darmstadt. C\u1ea3 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y gi\u1eefa 2 \u0111\u1ed9i, Darmstadt \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1eafng, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n n\u00e0o.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2193","checkdouble":"194168"},{"date":"11:53 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Guimaraes 02h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-benfica-vs-guimaraes-02h30-ngay-118-vdqg-bo-dao-nha-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Benfica vs Guimaraes l\u00fac 02h30 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 1 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha B\u0110N 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Guimaraes 02h30 ng\u00e0y 118 V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Guimaraes 02h30 ng\u00e0y 118 V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Benfica-vs-Guimaraes.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Benfica vs Guimaraes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left;\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Benfica vs Guimaraes: 2-0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Gi\u1eefa tu\u1ea7n sau Benfica ph\u1ea3i h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 trong tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u00f2ng s\u01a1 lo\u1ea1i th\u1ee9 3 Champions League v\u1edbi Fenerbahce n\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a cho v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u1edbi Vitoria Guimaraes. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf th\u00ec ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n 1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Rui Vitoria \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Guimaraes l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Benfica \u0111\u00e3 to\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong c\u1ea3 9 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean th\u1eafng c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t. S\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00f5, l\u1ea1i th\u00eam \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi tay Benfica.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, Vitoria Guimaraes d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c sau lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu (4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 1 h\u00f2a sau 5 tr\u1eadn), th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 b\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf C\u00fap Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p 1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Tondela, th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng Vitoria Guimaraes \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu thua 0-2 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTh\u00eam n\u1eefa, Vitoria Guimaraes c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u1ebft b\u00e1t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua t\u1edbi 9/10 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t. Xem ra kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd tr\u1eafng tay \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1ea1i Da Luz l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTH\u00c0NH T\u00cdCH \u0110\u1ed0I \u0110\u1ea6U<br />\r\n* 10 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi Vitoria Guimaraes, Benfica th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 1<br />\r\n* 10 l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, Benfica c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng 9, h\u00f2a 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Vitoria Guimaraes<br />\r\n* Benfica to\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf 9 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Vitoria Guimaraes t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, 6 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u 2 b\u00e0n.<br />\r\n* L\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, Benfica th\u1eafng 2-0 khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Vitoria Guimaraes.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTH\u00d4NG TIN L\u1ef0C L\u01af\u1ee2NG<br />\r\nBenfica: V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Jonas \u0111ang g\u1eb7p tr\u1ee5c tr\u1eb7c; Nicolas Castillo d\u00ednh \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2; Filip Krovinovic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br />\r\nVitoria Guimaraes: C\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 Pedro Henriques v\u00e0 Fernando Ven\u00e2ncio c\u00f9ng Welthon c\u00f2n b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2192","checkdouble":"194169"},{"date":"07:16 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nancy vs Lens 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-nancy-vs-lens-01h00-ngay-118-hang-2-phap-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nancy vs Lens l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8 (V\u00f2ng 3 gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p Ligue 2 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nancy vs Lens 01h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nancy vs Lens 01h00 ng\u00e0y 118 H\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Nancy_vs_Lens.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nancy vs Lens</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span>Nancy vs Lens: 0-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0ng Nancy l\u1ea1i thua c\u1ea3 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, \u0111\u1ec1u tr\u01b0\u1edbc hai \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00ean Ligue 2: Beziers v\u00e0 Paris FC. H\u1ecd ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn trong khi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eadn 4 b\u00e0n thua v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o, Nancy hi\u1ec7n x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH. S\u1ef1 u \u00e1m \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u bao quanh SV\u0110 Stade Marcel-Picot. S\u1ef1 gian kh\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Nancy c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i k\u00e9o d\u00e0i v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y khi h\u1ecd d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, Lens.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a 2017/18 di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Lens khi h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 14 chung cu\u00f4c t\u1ea1i Ligue 2. Tuy v\u1eady, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Lens \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 2 Ph\u00e1p m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n6 \u0111i\u1ec3m, 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o c\u00e0ng t\u00f4 \u0111\u1eadm c\u00f9ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Lens. Tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Lens c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Nancy \u0111\u00eam nay.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2191","checkdouble":"194146"},{"date":"08:55 10/08","title":"M\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00e2n binh, Alexis Sanchez ng\u1ea7m ch\u00ea MU \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Fred s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ed1n \u0111ang tr\u1ed1ng v\u1eafng \u1edf Old Trafford.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf Anh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng d\u00e0nh cho Man Utd, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o n\u1eefa trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i v\u00f4 danh nh\u01b0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot hay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Lee Grant, Fred tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m 25 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Old Trafford trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Fred c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Alexis Sanchez t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile: \u201cFred \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Andreas Pereira mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u2018jogo bonito\u2019 \u2013 th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p trong ti\u1ebfng Brazil hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng \u1edf MU.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1ebd Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y, ng\u1ea7m ch\u00ea bai ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi m\u1ed9t HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n, thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ra sao trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi xua tan \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u th\u00e0nh ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Old Trafford c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Premier League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2190","checkdouble":"194148"},{"date":"07:45 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u th\u00e0nh ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Old Trafford c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Premier League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sai \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m n\u00fap b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Man City v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, Man United h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua trong h\u00e8, ngay c\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4 Premier League c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Preview-Man-Utd-vs-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 \u1edf M\u1ef9 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, khi Man Utd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c, t\u1eeb li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn thua Bayer Munich hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-4 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 xen gi\u1eefa c\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 r\u1ed1i ren t\u1eeb tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00ean lu\u00f4n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng Old Trafford. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n hay th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9, tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Jose Mourinho hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n \u0111ang m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU v\u00e0 sau ng\u00e0y deadline 9/8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u201cc\u01a1m kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh, canh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ecdt\u201d v\u1edbi ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward v\u00ec c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u0169 trang, \u1ea5y th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam ba t\u00e2n binh, v\u1edbi hai trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Nhan-dinh-MU-vs-Leicester-(2h00-ngay-118)-Van-su-khoi-dau-nan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201cl\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n\u201d m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a Mourinho khi \u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u00e1c CLB trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ra \u0111i trong th\u1ebf c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c Premier League khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 HLV x\u1ee9 B\u1ed3 trong n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i y\u00ean \u1eafng khi\u1ebfn Man Utd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng Matic, Herrera, Rojo, Valencia hay t\u00e2n binh Dalot, trong khi nh\u1eefng Pogba, Lukaku, Lingard, Young hay Fellaini c\u0169ng b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n. Li\u1ec7u th\u00f3i quen kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u00f3 l\u1ea1i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn cho h\u1ecd khi b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Leicester tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m g\u00ec h\u01a1n. B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n v\u00e0 nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed chi ti\u00eau nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn mang t\u00ean Riyad Marez.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maguire cua Leicester\" title=\"Maguire cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Harry-Maguire-muon-den-MU-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia tay ng\u00f4i sao nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria sang Man City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Leicester ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng suy y\u1ebfu tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed3 chi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Rachid Ghezzal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i t\u1eeb Monaco m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u01b0 Jamie Vardy hay Harry Maguire v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n sau khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u00c7a\u011flar S\u00f6y\u00fcnc\u00fc c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd hay kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y deadline, Leicester s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i t\u1eeb tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 \u1edf Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u0169ng \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 6/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Man Utd. V\u1eady n\u00ean, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m xua tan m\u00e2y m\u00f9 \u1edf Old Trafford l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd (4-3-3): 1. De Gea; 36. Darmian \u2013 3. Bailly \u2013 12. Smalling \u2013 23. Shaw; 39. McTominay \u2013 17. Fred \u2013 15. Pereira; 8. Mata \u2013 10. Rashford \u2013 7. Sanchez<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Leicester (4-2-3-1): Schmeichel; Pereira \u2013 Morgan \u2013 Evans \u2013 Chilwell; Ndidi \u2013 Iborra, Diabate \u2013 Maddison \u2013 Albrighton; Iheanacho<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Nhan-dinh-MU-vs-Leicester-(2h00-ngay-118)-Van-su-khoi-dau-nan-hinh-anh-4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester: 2-1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham-172-193964.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham-172-193964.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Premier League 2018/19: Mou m\u00f9a 3 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea3m?</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ee5 n\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m NHA 2018/19 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2189","checkdouble":"194151"},{"date":"08:47 10/08","title":"Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/Pogba-va-Mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Barcelona song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Man United. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a 2017/18 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarcelona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Pogba v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Juventus c\u0169ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Mourinho-tiet-lo-Paul-Pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau khi chi\u1ec1u mua t\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i, M.U v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Pogba \u1edf l\u1ea1i trong \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho tin Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2. C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Pogba r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y qua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba va Mourinho\" title=\"Pogba va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Pogba-va-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1ebf n\u00e0o c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Ashley Young, Marouane Fellaini, Jesse Lingard. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi (v\u1edbi Leicester) hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ecdi ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Pogba r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c xem h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t tay hay kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2188","checkdouble":"194152"},{"date":"08:59 10/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: MU chia tay trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/chinh-thuc-fosumensah-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Timothy Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Fosu-Mensah l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Anh ra s\u00e2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSao tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Crystal Palace. \u1ede th\u00e0nh London, Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 21 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/CHINH-THUC-Fosu-Mensah-roi-MU-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU \u0111\u1ebfn Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Fosu-Mensah l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00e1c. Chia s\u1ebb sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Craven Cottage, Fosu-Mensah cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Fulham c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fulham t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tony Khan c\u1ee7a Fulham t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng Fulham \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Fosu-Mensah theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Man United. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i Premier League\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Fulham \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Jean-Michael Seri, Maxime Le Marchand, Alfie Mawson, Fabri, Joe Bryan v\u00e0 Aleksandar Mitrovic theo d\u1ea1ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t b\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, The Cottagers c\u00f2n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Andre Schurrle, Calum Chambers, Luciano Vietto v\u00e0 Sergio Rico theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/fosumensah-chung-chac-o-tuoi-18-172-131353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Man United</span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2187","checkdouble":"194154"}]}